{"tid":563001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一群人坐埋一齊食飯 講一陣去邊玩但係無叫埋你 你會唔會跟埋去?","createTime":"2018-02-16T12:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T16:42:49.000Z","uid":137997,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1d4c37cec5c087db2f3d6c20f2a36da4265ad7cc","tid":563001,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:32:26.000Z","msg":"有無巴打絲打試過咁樣?你地通常會唔會跟埋去<br />\n我自己試過幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同班朋友食完飯定唔知點樣走埋左一齊 諗緊有咩下半場通常都唔會問我意見我自己又諗唔到咩好意見 最後會去左食糖水睇戲定去邊到玩之類 我跟埋去又唔見佢地會反感咁 影相都會一齊影<br />\n <br />\n但係就係果個時候我特別無野講 又無人會叫我問我一唔一齊去 特別無存在感咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩方法可以預防呢類型既事發生"},{"pid":"10588b2d2bbbd9765beaea5dc68c08c001c3e0ff","tid":563001,"uid":26406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:33:46.000Z","msg":"唔好搞鳩人地啦"},{"pid":"c14c279db7c8449f9a725edb1c767fd44ad72da4","tid":563001,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:34:53.000Z","msg":"搭下爹"},{"pid":"424fd167ed9b8869f8e73169c2bf86f7d3cceb91","tid":563001,"uid":27049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6dfa62e01c6689d363150b6737a431a3f39ee6","tid":563001,"uid":10441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"熟唔熟先 熟既你又唔出聲就當你無意見架啦<br />\n咁唔會次次都問哂全部人意見架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37b74332bfe1ac2b991972d6d50de0b2e6ad1e3","tid":563001,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:36:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85b85818c5b00d894a134f482afd4951c364400b","tid":563001,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"自己醒水話眼訓返屋企先啦"},{"pid":"86490443ce102e80df266de1f4805329ac9afcd6","tid":563001,"uid":153518,"lik